>>> +               drm_err(&vma->vm->i915->drm,
>>> +                       "Failed to get pages for VMA view type %u (%d)!\n",
>>> +                       vma->ggtt_view.type, ret);
>> Can we just return here?
Yeah, should be harmless. Out of paranoia I set pages to 0 below.
